{"tid":1778570,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[工會戰線] 政府大春袋—醫療業界工會 要人！","createTime":"2019-12-11T05:10:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T05:53:25.000Z","uid":30862,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"423b4bc1760facd7501bce4cc84ce2b91a7017d3","tid":1778570,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T05:10:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/opuK9dH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FopuK9dH.jpg&h=13923bce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rQn8Rr8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrQn8Rr8.jpg&h=ecf5cd65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今晚係醫療界工會既集氣大會<br />\n7-9pm 愛丁堡<br />\n有不反架啦 無論係咪醫護界都可以去架<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n知道大家都對集會既成效有保留<br />\n驚會好左膠 <br />\n但想講既係 今晚係壯大工會戰線既好時機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家工會戰線已經逐漸成形 好多行業都刊憲成立左<br />\n最難個步&mdash;開頭 都已經有手足做左 冇理由唔入工會掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最難個步&mdash;開頭 都已經有手足做左 冇理由唔入工會掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最難個步&mdash;開頭 都已經有手足做左 冇理由唔入工會掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然已經有網上交表入工會 但現場都會有form比大家填 所以不同年齡層既同行都可以入架！<br />\n其他工會都會順勢宣傳！<br />\n<br />\n如果大家自認和理非 衝唔到既話 咁請盡和理非既責任<br />\n加入工會 配合罷工 會係和理非最強武器<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都係個句<br />\n大人肯罷工 細路唔洗衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n12月了 仲未入tg channel既 我唔會屌您<br />\n我會邀請您入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n⚠️罷工日程表更新⚠️<br />\n‼️二百萬三罷最新消息‼️<br />\n<br />\n1209-1213 會計界 和你帶 <br />\n1211 愛丁堡廣場醫療工會集氣大會 <br />\n1213 香港白領同行工會 尖沙咀街站 <br />\n1214 香港白領同行工會 觀塘及荔枝角街站 <br />\n1215 愛丁堡廣場社福罷工造勢大會<br />\n1216 香港舞台藝術從業員工會座談會 <br />\n1217-1219 社福界警告式罷工三天 <br />\n1220 香港白領同行工會 中環街站 <br />\n<br />\n⚠️工會籌組情況(9/12)⚠️<br />\n<br />\n已正式刊憲成立（10）：會計、金融、IT、保險、公務員、酒店、港鐵、言語治療、醫管局、白領<br />\n已收到職工局確認（1）：檢測及認證業、建築工程<br />\n已交表（12）：舞台藝術界、設計界、視光、製造業、航空、市場營銷管理、合約制非公務員、採購及貿易、職業治療、自由工作者、零售<br />\n準備交表（2）：影音界、製藥<br />\n籌備中（9）：廣告界、公關、物流、教育、幼教、髮型界、傳媒及出版、貿發局、人力資源<br />\n組隊中未夠人（5）：私家診所、快餐業、地產界、牙科界、航運<br />\nTotal（38）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n⚠️重要任務⚠️<br />\nTask 1 和你like<br />\n✳️目標：FB page 30k like✳️<br />\n✴️進度：8.8k/30k✴️<br />\nlink： <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2YiRz6G\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2YiRz6G&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDws2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=4f08705f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2YiRz6G</a><br />\n<br />\nTask 2 和你貼<br />\n✳️目標：各區連儂牆增加有關工會以及罷工的文宣✳️<br />\n<br />\nTask 3 和你入工會<br />\n✳️目標：新工會嘅入會率達行業10%✳️<br />\n詳情請按此 <br />\n<br />\n籌備工會支援 請聯絡 @historywillabsolveme 或 @sellbbq<br />\n其他查詢 請聯絡 @proundtobehker 或 @sugdh<br />\n----<br />\n🔴二百萬三罷聯合陣線🔴<br />\n抗爭 | 工會  | 罷工 | 行業行動<br />\n<br />\n頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDws2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=29990eca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike</a><br />\n各行業總Group list <a href=\"https://t.me/hkonstrike/478\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkonstrike%2F478&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDws2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=b67b0a79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkonstrike/478</a><br />\nFB <a href=\"https://bit.ly/2JQLM2f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2JQLM2f&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDws2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=0c29ad9a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2JQLM2f</a><br />\nIG <a href=\"https://bit.ly/33hmGRR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F33hmGRR&d=doP1hY1jTMShcZ7HAjrDws2proQWM4oxojYLcFbEfDU%3D&h=53a67d00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/33hmGRR</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命 唔係一個口號<br />\n就好似愛咁 講係冇用既<br />\n做啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 今晚見 入工會<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />: 繼續好嬲好嬲/做返港豬算"},{"pid":"6127118906a0fd32f8fca9412d11b79885e31e3a","tid":1778570,"uid":30862,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T05:10:54.000Z","msg":"大人肯罷工<br />\n細路唔洗衝"},{"pid":"9cacfb9ac51127d82409675d0d30556bf3d7f01b","tid":1778570,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T05:11:23.000Z","msg":"半年啦<br />\n我地要進化"},{"pid":"d83693a1f93dcc1b1261c0c4a1a558915da09c73","tid":1778570,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T05:11:40.000Z","msg":"工會戰線要人"},{"pid":"4c17f2e3955851de8673f0c1125a779a0864756f","tid":1778570,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T05:13:07.000Z","msg":"和理非都好多野可以做！！"},{"pid":"9b599cfe25a08e311b9a2a143e4fdaae084eff41","tid":1778570,"uid":30862,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T05:13:42.000Z","msg":"唔逼爆愛丁堡 唔緊要<br />\n<br />\n入工會就得"},{"pid":"aae845c7d919a64ffcc50cfee70f75b7d748c1a4","tid":1778570,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T05:14:31.000Z","msg":"工會既工業行動 <br />\n將會係半年既新戰幔"},{"pid":"8624ac1c202f72cf6c1dcec6fe30aa89acabac5a","tid":1778570,"uid":158,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T05:15:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"01acf85d0527755f7978275b78bf75d146673a0d","tid":1778570,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T05:15:18.000Z","msg":"和你shop以外<br />\n仲有和你join"},{"pid":"8d4ab72018f89392acb98cdf0a92793de3ccf10a","tid":1778570,"uid":45975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T05:15:23.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0280819d0522bff90133da190d403f078183f737","tid":1778570,"uid":30862,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8624ac1c202f72cf6c1dcec6fe30aa89acabac5a","tid":177